<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,minimum-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no" />
		<title></title>
		<script src="../js/mui.min.js"></script>
		<link href="../css/mui.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
		<script type="text/javascript" charset="UTF-8">
			mui.init();
		</script>
		<style type="text/css">
			.verify_header {
				background: #00418F;
			}
			
			.verify_header h1,
			.verify_header a {
				color: #FFFFFF;
			}
			
			.mui-row {
				text-align: center;
			}
			
			.mui-account-title {
				padding-top: 20px;
				color: rgb(51,51,51);
				font-size: 20px;
				margin-bottom: 30px;
			}
			.mui-account p{
				text-align: center;
				line-height: 12px;
				padding: 0 18px;
			}
			
			.mui-account-div{
				border-bottom: 1px solid #CCCCCC;
				padding: 0;
				margin: 0;
				margin: 0 18px;
			}
			.mui-account-div-last{
			}
		</style>
	</head>

	<body>
		<header class="mui-bar mui-bar-nav" style="background-color: #0066FF">
			<a class="mui-icon mui-icon-arrowleft h-left mui-action-back" style="color: #fff;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">返回</span></a>
			<h1 class="mui-title" style="color: #fff;font-size: 16px;">了解独立资金账户</h1>
		</header>
		<div class="mui-content mui-account" style="background: #ffffff;">
			<div class="mui-row">
				<img src="../images/zijin1.png" style="width: 100%;margin-top: 50px;" />
			</div>
			<div class="mui-row mui-content-padded">

				<img src="../images/zijin2.png" style="width: 70%;margin: 0px 0;" />
				<div class="mui-account-title">
					独立资金账户
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="mui-account-div">
				<p style="padding: 0;">中信银行针对每个企业用户</p>
				<p style="margin-bottom: 40px;padding: 0;">单独设立资金账户， 资金更安全。</p>
			</div>

			<div class="mui-row mui-content-padded" style="margin-top: 40px;">
				<img src="../images/zijin3.png" style="width: 70%;" />
				<div class="mui-account-title">
					资金记录透明
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="mui-account-div">
				<p style="padding: 0;">每笔交易都可在"中信银行——公司网上银行"</p>
				<p style="padding: 0;">上直接打印出银行回单，保障资金进出记录全</p>
				<p style="padding: 0;">透明， 企业用户也可以随时到中信银行柜台领</p>
				<p style="padding: 0;margin-bottom: 40px;">取U盾或打印纸质回单。</p>
			</div>
			<div class="mui-row mui-content-padded" style="margin-top: 40px;">
				<div id="">
					<img src="../images/zijin4.png" style="width: 70%;" />
				</div>
				<div class="mui-account-title">
					用户资金更安全
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="mui-account-div">
				<p style="padding: 0;">隔离了用户的交易资金和平台自有资金，</p>
				<p style="padding: 0;">银承库只负责保存用户信息，</p>
				<p style="padding: 0;margin-bottom: 40px;">不能动用用户资金。</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="mui-row mui-content-padded">

				<img src="../images/zijin5.png" style="width: 70%;" />
				<div class="mui-account-title">
					避免风险
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="mui-account-div-last">
				<p style="padding: 0;">避免了平台跑路、资金池以及资金往来</p>
				<p style="padding: 0;">不透明的风险。</p>
			</div>
			<div style="height: 40px;">
				
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>

</html>